headline: 3 Low-Volatility Stocks That Concern Us
summary: A stock with low volatility can be reassuring, but it doesn’t always mean strong long-term performance. Investors who prioritize stability may miss out on higher-reward opportunities elsewhere.

headline: AT&T Amazon Cloud And Satellite Deals Reframe Fiber And Broadband Story
summary: AT&T (NYSE:T) has announced new partnerships with Amazon Web Services and Amazon Leo to modernize U.S. connectivity. The collaboration focuses on linking AWS data centers with AT&T’s high capacity fiber network. Amazon Leo will work with AT&T to extend fixed broadband into underserved areas across the country.
